      <h2>Interactive Quiz Application</h2>
      <p>
        This project is an interactive quiz application designed to test users'
        knowledge on various topics. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, it
        offers a dynamic user experience with real-time feedback and scoring.
      </p>

      <div class="project-images">
        <img src="screensort1.png" alt="Quiz Application Screenshot 1" />
        <img src="screensort2.png" alt="Quiz Application Screenshot 2" />
      </div>

      <div class="project-details">
        <h3>Technologies Used:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>HTML5</li>
          <li>CSS3</li>
          <li>JavaScript</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Project Objective:</h3>
        <p>
          The objective of this project was to design and develop an interactive
          quiz application that provides users with an engaging way to test
          their knowledge on various topics. The application was intended to be
          user-friendly, responsive, and capable of delivering immediate
          feedback, enhancing the learning experience. It aimed to combine
          educational content with a fun, interactive interface, making it
          suitable for users of all ages.
        </p>

        <h3>Process:</h3>
        <p>
          After researching quiz applications, I designed the layout using
          wireframes, then developed the frontend using HTML and CSS. JavaScript
          was used to handle user interactions and scoring logic.
        </p>

        <h3>Outcome:</h3>
        <p>
          The final application is a fully responsive and interactive quiz that
          provides users with instant feedback and tracks their scores.
        </p>
      </div>

